---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy | Sight Words"
  description="Read the privacy policy for this free sight word website, including cookies, analytics, and how data is used."
  canonicalUrl="https://sightwordspractice.com/privacy-policy"
>
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>

  <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
    This page explains what information this website collects and how it is used. We keep things simple and
    privacy-friendly so parents, teachers, and children can use the site with confidence.
  </p>

  <section class="space-y-6 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
    <div>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">What We Collect</h2>
      <p>
        We may collect basic website analytics, such as which pages are visited, how long visitors stay, and what
        device type is used. This information is usually collected in aggregate and does not directly identify you.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">No Accounts or Personal Data Collection</h2>
      <p>
        This site does not have user accounts, logins, or profile features. We do not ask for names, email addresses,
        phone numbers, or other personal details directly through the site.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Cookies</h2>
      <p>
        Cookies are small text files saved by your browser. They can help websites remember basic settings and support
        analytics tools. On this site, cookies may be used for simple performance and usage tracking.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p>
        We may use third-party analytics services (for example, Google Analytics) to understand how the site is used.
        These tools may set their own cookies and process usage data under their own privacy policies.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">How Data Is Used</h2>
      <p>
        Any analytics data is used to improve the website, such as making pages easier to use, improving content,
        and fixing performance issues.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Children's Use</h2>
      <p>
        This site is designed for educational use by families and schools. Because we do not provide accounts or
        direct personal data entry, children can use the site safely without submitting personal information.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Policy Updates</h2>
      <p>
        We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any updates will be posted on this page with the latest
        version replacing the previous one.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
